:521601,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:05:48.000Z","msg":"冇嘢做架 扑嘢啦"},{"pid":"3d237e5bed229dbef3128430a6d45c203e802def","tid":521601,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:10:19.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c9dece0efda71c4a5d76c0e337ae5cfc5d24167c","tid":521601,"uid":58068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"aia"},{"pid":"4ccab70c2712b2ca2d92352e5b83f41bb3da9610","tid":521601,"uid":3203,"like":67,"dislike":5,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T18:38:57.000Z","msg":"第一次先唔好比到佢悶既感覺<br />\n亦唔好比人覺得你mk<br />\n<br />\n所以博物館/圖書館/展覽/唱k 黎d就盡量唔好喇<br />\n<br />\n除非,佢提議/提起過<br />\n<br />\n咁睇戲黎樣其實又唔係咁好<br />\n<br />\n因為幾捉心理<br />\n<br />\n你又未清楚佢中意睇咩戲,你以為佢中意卡通片但原來唔係既,買錯就唔抵<br />\n<br />\n如果跟你興趣,可能佢又唔like<br />\n<br />\n尤其男仔比較中意動作/科幻/驚奇/懸疑片<br />\n<br />\n未係個個女仔接受到<br />\n<br />\n咁如果經濟負擔到<br />\n<br />\n咪去下主題公園玩lo<br />\n<br />\n不過都總有危機<br />\n<br />\n第一如果去迪士尼公園<br />\n<br />\n可能佢會覺得你幼稚<br />\n<br />\n第二如果去海馬公園<br />\n<br />\n佢又未必玩機動遊戲<br />\n<br />\n無理由比幾百蚊入去睇海獅對手起到啪啪啪架麻<br />\n<br />\n咁所以你都係帶佢返屋企啪啪啪喇<br />\n<br />\n一黎比到佢覺得你重視佢,第一次就帶佢返屋企<br />\n<br />\n二黎慳錢,比佢睇到你係一個好男人<br />\n<br />\n三黎活動老少鹹宜,特別係你黎d鹹濕仔"},{"pid":"b8c915c7b7adc194bbfa488d61bb504f4c740de1","tid":521601,"uid":85633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/012029_d516a26fe49066a7ed7de882767e523d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F012029_d516a26fe49066a7ed7de882767e523d.png&h=750b8930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前cap低 可供參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有cap低呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09181053af1eb412f1431c05f92