曬好攰<br />\n泛舟睇日落，條女就會怨好多蚊呀好攰呀<br />\nBbq 條女就會話自己俾錢煮野食成件事好on9<br />\n但最辛苦都只會係樓主，因為踩單車會變成踩家庭單車，得樓主一個踩載埋條女，泛舟睇日落都只會得樓主一個撐，直落bbq仲要燒埋野食俾條女，仲要俾人嫌佢燒得燶，但係以上洗費仲要樓主一個出，出錢又出力，最後仲要送埋條女返屋企"},{"pid":"5fa3cd2c4d189123cc053de2528bcecf0e1d5d33","tid":521601,"uid":139652,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T21:31:50.000Z","msg":"日日同女朋友匿喺屋企睇電視 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85076372be3b7f26a90c965c8f28708c87e617c","tid":521601,"uid":95499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d253a58bf1c37c10e4d19e70693f0001c96faf8","tid":521601,"uid":34177,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T17:21:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/012029_d516a26fe49066a7ed7de882767e523d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F012029_d516a26fe49066a7ed7de882767e523d.png&h=750b8930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前cap低 可供參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T22:10:17.000Z","msg":"係咪cap漏咗打差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}